title: Alvin and the Chipmunks take on Star Wars: The Force Awakens in a release date battle doomed to end badly - Movies
text: The next Alvin and the Chipmunks movie will be squaring off against Star Wars: The Force Awakens at the box office.In the US, Alvin and the Chipmunks: The Road Chip has been moved from December 23 to December 18. Â© 20th Century FoxAlvin and the Chipmunks: The Road Chip Sisters, starring Tina Fey and Amy Poehler, will also launch on the same date.The fourth entry in the CGI/live-action series, Road Chip follows the Chipmunks (Justin Long, Matthew Gray Gubler, Jesse McCartney) as they try to stop Dave (Jason Lee) from proposing to his new girlfriend.Christina Applegate, Anna Faris, Kaley Cuoco, Bella Thorne and Tony Hale also star.Watch a trailer for Alvin and the Chipmunks: The Road Chip below:
